5.0','2025-03-06 10:53:06','admin','2025-03-06 00:00:00','2025-03-04 00:00:00',0,'0','System Auto Run','2025-04-01 13:22:31','0',1,100,'&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-success&quot;&gt;Program Details&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Chiang Mai province &amp;ndash; Northern Thailand&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nearest Airport:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Chiang Mai (CNX)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Half Day Afternoon&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please see the Availability Calendar - Select your preferred date to Book Now !&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elephant Nature Park is a sanctuary for many rescued elephants, enabling them to live out their lives in their own social groups, roaming the pasture freely.&lt;br&gt;The half-day afternoon program at Elephant Nature Park offers a unique opportunity to spend quality time observing and being with the magnificent elephant herd. We prioritise creating a relaxed and immersive experience, allowing visitors to truly appreciate and learn from these incredible creatures.&lt;/p&gt;',1),(6,'โปรแกรม','Program Package Ticker ','2','THB',1,'2025-03-17 09:04:53',1,'admin','นายAdmin 5.0','2025-03-17 09:04:53',1,'admin','นายAdmin 5.0','1','นายAdmin 5.0','2025-03-17 09:04:53','admin','2025-03-17 00:00:00','2025-03-04 00:00:00',0,'0','System Auto Run','2025-04-01 13:22:31','0',1,100,'&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-success&quot;&gt;Program Details&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Chiang Mai province &amp;ndash; Northern Thailand&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nearest Airport:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Chiang Mai (CNX)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Half Day Afternoon&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please see the Availability Calendar - Select your preferred date to Book Now !&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elephant Nature Park is a sanctuary for many rescued elephants, enabling them to live out their lives in their own social groups, roaming the pasture freely.&lt;br&gt;The half-day afternoon program at Elephant Nature Park offers a unique opportunity to spend quality time observing and being with the magnificent elephant herd. We prioritise creating a relaxed and immersive experience, allowing visitors to truly appreciate and learn from these incredible creatures.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-success&quot;&gt;Program Details&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Starting From:&amp;nbsp;12:00 pm - 12:30 pm - We offer convenient pick-up from your Chiang Mai city hotel. Alternatively, you can meet us at our office at 11:45 am -&amp;nbsp;(Please check map)&amp;nbsp;If you are staying out of town (outside Middle ring-road) additional charges apply. Please advise on your reservation form.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2:00 pm - Arrival at Elephant Nature Park.&amp;nbsp;Embark on a guided walk with our knowledgeable staff and the elephants, emphasising a no-riding policy. We will take you to the river that skirts the park, where you can observe and learn about the elephants&amp;acute; habitat and history.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4:00 pm - Snack Break:&amp;nbsp;Indulge in a delicious assortment of snacks, seasonal fruits, and refreshing drinks specially prepared for your group. Take this opportunity to enjoy the view of the elephant herd from our elevated platform&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;5:00 pm - It&amp;acute;s time to bid farewell to the elephants and Elephant Nature Park, as we begin the hour-long drive back to Chiang Mai. We will drop you off at your hotel or our ENP office, as per your preference&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-success&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-success&quot;&gt;Included in the Program&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meals:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Snacks, seasonal fruits, and a variety of beverages such as tea, coffee, and soft drinks.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transportation:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We provide convenient round-trip transportation between Chiang Mai city office and Elephant Nature Park.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Admission Fees:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;All necessary entrance fees are included for your visit to Elephant Nature Park.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Park Guides:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Knowledgeable guides will accompany you throughout the program, offering valuable insights and information about the park and its resident elephants.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Insurance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;We invite you to join us at Elephant Nature Park, where you can connect with these majestic creatures and experience an unforgettable morning filled with wonder and learning.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;',1),(7,'Program Package Ticker Special','Program Package Ticker Special','1','THB',1,'2025-03-19 14:20:27',1,'admin','นายAdmin 5.0','2025-03-19 14:20:27',1,'admin','นายAdmin 5.0','1','นายAdmin 5.0','2025-03-19 14:20:27','admin','2025-01-01 00:00:00','2025-03-04 00:00:00',0,'0','System Auto Run','2025-04-01 13:22:31','0',1,100,'&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.elephantnaturepark.org/enp/visit-volunteer/projects/overnight-elephant-nature-park-2days-1night-43/view&quot;&gt;ENP - Overnight (2 Days + 1 Night)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;project-snippet&quot;&gt;Sleepovers in the midst of a thriving elephant herd offers visitors the chance to enjoy the simple rustic nature of Northern Thailand in the unique company of our rescued herd. We pick up from your hotel for a scenic drive north to Elephant Nature Park where you will meet our magnificent elephant herd. Observe our herd at play and watch them interact in each of their social groups. Full dinner at the park and accommodation at park huts. After breakfast, walk to see the elephants roaming in the open pasture.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;project-snippet&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;project-s