vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Elephant Nature Park is a sanctuary for many rescued elephants, enabling them to live out their lives in their own social groups, roaming the pasture freely.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;The Half Day morning program offers a unique opportunity to spend quality time at Elephant Nature Park Sanctuary, observing and being with the magnificent elephant herd. We prioritize creating a relaxed and immersive experience, allowing visitors to truly appreciate and learn from these incredible creatures.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;This program warmly welcomes all visitors to Elephant Nature Park Sanctuary and offer facilities to accommodate wheelchair users. If you use a wheelchair or have specific accessibility needs, please contact us via email before booking our half-day tour. This allows us to ratify necessary details and ensure that your needs are accommodated. We do not however supply wheelchairs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Program Details:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Starting From:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; 7:30 am - 8:00 am - We offer convenient pick-up from your Chiang Mai city hotel. Alternatively, you can meet us at our office at 7:15 am - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;( &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a title=&quot;Please check map&quot; href=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/d/edit?mid=zRtxhEsQybgQ.k06JQDqP1Egs&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Please check map&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; )&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; If you are staying out of town ( &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a title=&quot;outside Middle ring-road&quot; href=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/d/edit?mid=zRtxhEsQybgQ.k06JQDqP1Egs&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;outside Middle ring-road&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; ) additional charges apply. Please advise on your reservation form.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;9:30 am - Arrival at Elephant Nature Park Sanctuary.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; Embark on a guided walk with our knowledgeable staff and the elephants, emphasizing a no-riding policy. We will take you to the river that skirts the park, where you can observe and learn about the elephants&amp;acute; habitat and history.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;12:00 noon - Lunch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; : Indulge in a healthy and diverse vegan buffet featuring a range of Asian and International dishes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;1:00 pm - After lunch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; , it&amp;acute;s time to bid farewell to the elephants and Elephant Nature Park, as we begin the hour-long drive back to Chiang Mai. We will drop you off at your hotel or our ENP office, as per your preference.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Included in the Program:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Meals:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; Enjoy a delectable vegan buffet lunch that offers a variety of dishes inspired by Asian and International cuisines.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Transportation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; We provide convenient round-trip transportation between Chiang Mai city office and Elephant Nature Park Sanctuary.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;